I"¶<p>Starting with 0.31 the <a href="/integrations/updater/">updater component</a> sends an optional report about Home Assistant instance.</p>
<p>If you want to opt-in to include integration information, add <code>include_used_components</code> to your config. This will allow the Home Assistant developers to focus development efforts on the most popular components.</p>
<pre><code class="language-yaml">updater:
  include_used_components: true
</code></pre>
<p>We are only collecting this information to better understand our user base to provide better long term support and feature development.</p>
